Requirements:
-------------
To play this game you need to original PC version of either
"Gold Edition" or "Classic 2000 Edition".
Classic 2000 Edition can still be bought on Steam and features background
music while playing the game.

You also need to have PowerSDL for MorphOS installed.
You can find it on Aminet at: http://aminet.net/package/util/libs/powersdl



Installation:
-------------
Just run the game and let the installer do the work.
Alternatively, you can just copy the original game files into the main drawer.



Sourcecode:
-----------
Complete sourcecode for the game and statically linked libraries are
available on Aminet at: http://aminet.net/package/game/shoot/avp.src-morphos



History:
--------
1.00 - Initial release.




